| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5869 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 88e7e533-aa9a-549b-8f1f-2b51b5a8bd33"
